    <title>Atom Usage</title>
    <link href="http://luminoid.github.io/blog/2017/06/12/Atom-Usage/"/>
    <id>http://luminoid.github.io/blog/2017/06/12/Atom-Usage/</id>
    <published>2017-06-12T10:04:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-12T11:26:23.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- toc -->
<h2 id="Shortcut"><a href="#Shortcut" class="headerlink" title="Shortcut"></a>Shortcut</h2><p><code>cmd-shift-L</code>: Split selections into lines<br><code>ctrl-cmd-up</code>, <code>ctrl-cmd-down</code>: Move line up or down<br><code>cmd-d</code>: Duplicate lines<br><code>ctrl-shift-K</code>: Delete line<br><a id="more"></a><br><code>cmd-K-U</code>: Upper case the current word<br><code>cmd-K-L</code>: Lower case the current word<br><code>cmd-D</code>: Select the next word in the document that is the same as the currently selected word<br><code>cmd-shift-f</code>: Search the entire project<br><code>alt-cmd-[</code> and <code>alt-cmd-]</code>: Fold or unfold the code</p>
<h2 id="Packages"><a href="#Packages" class="headerlink" title="Packages"></a>Packages</h2><h3 id="Tool"><a href="#Tool" class="headerlink" title="Tool"></a>Tool</h3><h4 id="platformio-ide-terminal"><a href="#platformio-ide-terminal" class="headerlink" title="platformio-ide-terminal"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/platformio-ide-terminal" target="_blank" rel="external">platformio-ide-terminal</a></h4><p>A terminal package for Atom, complete with themes, API and more for PlatformIO IDE. Fork of terminal-plus.</p>
<h4 id="script"><a href="#script" class="headerlink" title="script"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/script" target="_blank" rel="external">script</a></h4><p>Run code in Atom</p>
<h4 id="linter"><a href="#linter" class="headerlink" title="linter"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/linter" target="_blank" rel="external">linter</a></h4><p>A Base Linter with Cow Powers</p>
<h4 id="hydrogen"><a href="#hydrogen" class="headerlink" title="hydrogen"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/Hydrogen" target="_blank" rel="external">hydrogen</a></h4><p>Run code and get results inline using Jupyter kernels like IPython, IJulia, and iTorch</p>
<h4 id="atom-beautify"><a href="#atom-beautify" class="headerlink" title="atom-beautify"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/atom-beautify" target="_blank" rel="external">atom-beautify</a></h4><p>Beautify HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, Python, Ruby, Java, C, C++, C#, Objective-C, CoffeeScript, TypeScript, Coldfusion, SQL, and more in Atom</p>
<h4 id="split-diff"><a href="#split-diff" class="headerlink" title="split-diff"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/split-diff" target="_blank" rel="external">split-diff</a></h4><p>A split pane diff tool.</p>
<h4 id="color-picker"><a href="#color-picker" class="headerlink" title="color-picker"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/color-picker" target="_blank" rel="external">color-picker</a></h4><p>Right click or press CMD-SHIFT-C/CTRL-ALT-C to open it.</p>
<h4 id="Busy-Signal"><a href="#Busy-Signal" class="headerlink" title="Busy Signal"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/busy-signal" target="_blank" rel="external">Busy Signal</a></h4><p>A package that provides an easy to use API to show your package is performing a task.</p>
<h4 id="browser-plus"><a href="#browser-plus" class="headerlink" title="browser-plus"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/browser-plus" target="_blank" rel="external">browser-plus</a></h4><p>Real Browser in ATOM</p>
<h3 id="UI"><a href="#UI" class="headerlink" title="UI"></a>UI</h3><h4 id="minimap"><a href="#minimap" class="headerlink" title="minimap"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/minimap" target="_blank" rel="external">minimap</a></h4><p>A preview of the full source code.</p>
<h4 id="file-icons"><a href="#file-icons" class="headerlink" title="file-icons"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/file-icons" target="_blank" rel="external">file-icons</a></h4><p>Assign file extension icons and colours for improved visual grepping</p>
<h4 id="highlight-selected"><a href="#highlight-selected" class="headerlink" title="highlight-selected"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/highlight-selected" target="_blank" rel="external">highlight-selected</a></h4><p>Highlights the current word selected when double clicking</p>
<h4 id="pigments"><a href="#pigments" class="headerlink" title="pigments"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/pigments" target="_blank" rel="external">pigments</a></h4><p>A package to display colors in project and files.</p>
<h4 id="qolor"><a href="#qolor" class="headerlink" title="qolor"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/qolor" target="_blank" rel="external">qolor</a></h4><p>An atom package to color your SQL queries!</p>
<h4 id="minimap-highlight-selected"><a href="#minimap-highlight-selected" class="headerlink" title="minimap-highlight-selected"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/minimap-highlight-selected" target="_blank" rel="external">minimap-highlight-selected</a></h4><p>A minimap binding for the highlight-selected package</p>
<h4 id="minimap-find-and-replace"><a href="#minimap-find-and-replace" class="headerlink" title="minimap-find-and-replace"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/minimap-find-and-replace" target="_blank" rel="external">minimap-find-and-replace</a></h4><p>Minimap bindings for the find and replace package</p>
<h4 id="minimap-pigments"><a href="#minimap-pigments" class="headerlink" title="minimap-pigments"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/minimap-pigments" target="_blank" rel="external">minimap-pigments</a></h4><p>An Atom plugin to display pigments colors in the Minimap.</p>
<h4 id="minimap-autohide"><a href="#minimap-autohide" class="headerlink" title="minimap-autohide"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/minimap-autohide" target="_blank" rel="external">minimap-autohide</a></h4><p>Automatically hide the minimap when you aren’t using it.</p>
<h3 id="Preview"><a href="#Preview" class="headerlink" title="Preview"></a>Preview</h3><h4 id="preview"><a href="#preview" class="headerlink" title="preview"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/preview" target="_blank" rel="external">preview</a></h4><p>Ultimate previewer of source code in Atom.</p>
<h4 id="markdown-preview-enhanced"><a href="#markdown-preview-enhanced" class="headerlink" title="markdown-preview-enhanced"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/markdown-preview-enhanced" target="_blank" rel="external">markdown-preview-enhanced</a></h4><p>The ‘BEST’ Markdown Preview you need for Atom Editor!</p>
<h4 id="atom-html-preview"><a href="#atom-html-preview" class="headerlink" title="atom-html-preview"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/atom-html-preview" target="_blank" rel="external">atom-html-preview</a></h4><p>A live preview tool for Atom Editor.</p>
<h4 id="pdf-view"><a href="#pdf-view" class="headerlink" title="pdf-view"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/pdf-view" target="_blank" rel="external">pdf-view</a></h4><p>Atom PDF viewer based on PDF.js</p>
<h4 id="regex-railroad-diagram"><a href="#regex-railroad-diagram" class="headerlink" title="regex-railroad-diagram"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/regex-railroad-diagram" target="_blank" rel="external">regex-railroad-diagram</a></h4><p>Display railroad diagram of regex under cursor.</p>
<h4 id="hex"><a href="#hex" class="headerlink" title="hex"></a><a href="https://github.com/AbeEstrada/atom-hex" target="_blank" rel="external">hex</a></h4><p>View the hex dump of any file</p>
<h3 id="Language"><a href="#Language" class="headerlink" title="Language"></a>Language</h3><h4 id="language-markdown"><a href="#language-markdown" class="headerlink" title="language-markdown"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/language-markdown" target="_blank" rel="external">language-markdown</a></h4><p>Adds grammar support for Markdown</p>
<h4 id="language-babel"><a href="#language-babel" class="headerlink" title="language-babel"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/language-babel" target="_blank" rel="external">language-babel</a></h4><p>JavaScript ES201x, React JSX, Flow and GraphQL Grammar. Babel Transpiler</p>
<h4 id="autocomplete-python"><a href="#autocomplete-python" class="headerlink" title="autocomplete-python"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/autocomplete-python" target="_blank" rel="external">autocomplete-python</a></h4><p>Python completions for packages, variables, methods, functions, with their arguments. Powered by your choice of Jedi or Kite.</p>
<h4 id="autocomplete-clang"><a href="#autocomplete-clang" class="headerlink" title="autocomplete-clang"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/autocomplete-clang" target="_blank" rel="external">autocomplete-clang</a></h4><p>autocomplete for C/C++/ObjC using clang</p>
<h4 id="atom-ternjs"><a href="#atom-ternjs" class="headerlink" title="atom-ternjs"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/atom-ternjs" target="_blank" rel="external">atom-ternjs</a></h4><p>JavaScript code intelligence for atom with Tern. Adds support for ES5, ES6 (JavaScript 2015), Node.js, jQuery &amp; Angular.</p>
<h3 id="Web"><a href="#Web" class="headerlink" title="Web"></a>Web</h3><h4 id="emmet"><a href="#emmet" class="headerlink" title="emmet"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/emmet" target="_blank" rel="external">emmet</a></h4><p>Emmet – the essential tool for web developers</p>
<h4 id="atom-bootstrap4"><a href="#atom-bootstrap4" class="headerlink" title="atom-bootstrap4"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/atom-bootstrap4" target="_blank" rel="external">atom-bootstrap4</a></h4><p>Bootstrap4 Support with snippets and autocompletion.</p>
<h3 id="Git"><a href="#Git" class="headerlink" title="Git"></a>Git</h3><h4 id="gitignore-snippets"><a href="#gitignore-snippets" class="headerlink" title="gitignore-snippets"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/gitignore-snippets" target="_blank" rel="external">gitignore-snippets</a></h4><p>Quickly create .gitignore files with templates from GitHub.</p>
<h3 id="Coding"><a href="#Coding" class="headerlink" title="Coding"></a>Coding</h3><h4 id="base64"><a href="#base64" class="headerlink" title="base64"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/base64" target="_blank" rel="external">base64</a></h4><p>A Base64 encoder and decoder</p>
<h4 id="url-encode"><a href="#url-encode" class="headerlink" title="url-encode"></a><a href="https://atom.io/packages/url-encode" target="_blank" rel="external">url-encode</a></h4><p>URL encode or decode the selected text.</p>
]]></content>
    
