  <entry>
    <title>Hexo Quick Guide</title>
    <link href="http://luminoid.github.io/blog/2017/06/08/Hexo-Quick-Guide/"/>
    <id>http://luminoid.github.io/blog/2017/06/08/Hexo-Quick-Guide/</id>
    <published>2017-06-08T03:06:48.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-12T11:35:52.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- toc -->
<p><a href="https://hexo.io" target="_blank" rel="external">Hexo</a><br><a href="https://github.com/LouisBarranqueiro/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo-theme-tranquilpeak</a></p>
<h2 id="Quick-deploy"><a href="#Quick-deploy" class="headerlink" title="Quick deploy"></a>Quick deploy</h2><p>With Algolia<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Article"</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo clean</div><div class="line">$ hexo algolia</div><div class="line">$ hexo deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>Without Algolia<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Article"</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo deploy -g</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="Create"><a href="#Create" class="headerlink" title="Create"></a>Create</h2><p>Initializes a website.<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo init <span class="string">"My New Website"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>Create a new article.<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Article"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="Develop"><a href="#Develop" class="headerlink" title="Develop"></a>Develop</h2><p>Generate static files and watch file changes.<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo generate -w</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>Start a local server.<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo server</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>Index posts on Algolia. (This command runs without preceding <code>hexo generate</code>)<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo algolia</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="Deploy"><a href="#Deploy" class="headerlink" title="Deploy"></a>Deploy</h2><p>Deploys your website.<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;!-- toc --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://hexo.io&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Hexo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/LouisBarranqueiro/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;hexo-theme-tranquilpeak&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Quick-deploy&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Quick-deploy&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Quick deploy&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Quick deploy&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;With Algolia&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight bash&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ hexo new &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&quot;My New Article&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ hexo clean&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ hexo algolia&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ hexo deploy&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
